<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Razamatazz Pizzazz</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=adonhiram>Adonhiram</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 183<br> <font color=#333333>(2/26/03 7:12:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=565.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: If i am not a cannipetting mage is switch to Evoc. best </span><hr size=1> Just a quick note to say me too switched from Evoc to Conj at 59 (in expectation of SoFB), and now I am 62 and prefer to stick to Conj, than to switch back to Evoc and again to Conj at 63 for BS. All in all, even using a lot FBoT and Sun Storm, you still get benefits being Cong specced :<br>
